Class ROC.DistanceResultAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.evaluation.roc.ROC.DistanceResultAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ROC.DBIDRefIter, ROC.ScoreIter, Iter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ROC.FilteredDistanceResultAdapter
    Enclosing class:
    ROC

    public static class ROC.DistanceResultAdapter
extends Object
implements ROC.ScoreIter, ROC.DBIDRefIter
    This adapter is used to process a list of (double, DBID) objects. The list must be sorted appropriately, the score is only used to detect ties.
